    The Iquomi architecture is based around three main areas: individuals, groups and
    organizations. Each area could benefit by using Iquomi for their data queries.
    <p style="text-align: center">
        <img src="~/gfx/overview-grid.gif" width="480" height="408" runat="server" />
    </p>
    <b>For Individuals</b>
    <br />
    You as an individual who currently need to manage multiple devices each containing
    separate islands of data will benefit greatly, because Iquomi services can be accessed
    from any of them.
